Package de.hpi.bpt.chimera.database

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Connection
    This class is used to build a connection to the database.
    ConnectionWrapper
    This class knows the database credentials and provides a method to connect to the database.
    DbCaseStart  
    DbControlFlow
    Represents the ControlFlow in the database.
    DbEmailConfiguration
    This class is the representation of a E-mail configuration in the database.
    DbFragment
    This class is the representation of a fragment in the database.
    DbFragmentInstance
    This class is the representation of a fragment instance in the database.
    DbObject
    This class is the representation of a database object.
    DbPathMapping
    Class for database access to the mapping from data objects and their attributes to a specified json path.
    DbScenario
    This class represents the ScenarioData in the database.
    DbScenarioInstance
    This class administrates the scenario instances in the databases and provides check methods to make sure the database is correct.
    DbSelectedDataObjects
    This class is used to save and retrieve the data objects selected by the user to work on in an activity.
